the trials objective is to decide who is responsible for the 
murder of mendes on the night of dec 22 1988 
but some residents and traveling salesmen have other objectives 
mainly making quick bucks off the hundreds of ecologists 
politicians journalists and officials that have flocked to this 
town to see the trial 
anything is fair game for the face of the slain rain forest 
defender and rubber tapper he appears on buttons lags ashtrays 
can openers tshirts caps and wooden cups there are even chico 
mendes christmas cards going for 3 apiece 
how much cried ilzamar mendes widow of the slain ecologist 
and head of the chico mendes foundation i wouldnt even buy one 
at that price 
not many of the rubber tappers that live in this river town can 
the exploitation proves irritating to some especially for those 
like luiz vieira de souza a 63yearold tapper who traveled eight 
hours in a dugout canoe eating solely manioc root to get to xapuri 
this is crazy bristled the leatheryskinned tapper as he 
refused a bottle of mineral water selling for 1 i may have to 
leave early if my money runs out 
some profiteers are imaginative one barrelshaped elderly woman 
from brazils northern atlantic coastal state of bahia set up a 
stand in front of the town courthouse to sell shrimp stew 
shrimp in the amazon asked a visitor the gentle round 
woman called isaura smiled 
yes sir and just 2 per ladle she said 
down the dusty brick and cobblestone street zamir jose teixeira 
was loading a fourfoothigh chestnut tree into an oxdrawn cart 
the buyer was counting a wad of bills under a banner that said 
progress in the jungle 
had teixeira legally cut the trees no one knew and teixeira 
wasnt telling 
forest produce was a bit more reasonable if the buyer comparison 
shopped a 2ounce box of powdered guarana a tart amazon fruit 
used in its powdered form as a stimulant was selling for the 
equivalent of 5 
a plate of white rice red beans lettuce tomatoes and heavily 
salted beef seemed reasonable at 4 
did i say 500 cruzeiros asked the redfaced waitress with a 
giggle im sorry i meant 1500 
