a usmanufactured board game that uses derogatory 
language toward japanese minorities is being pulled from store 
shelves by its japanese distributor a company official said today 
the instruction manual for the game land of ninja uses a 
disparaging name for a former japanese outcast class and calls 
another minority group barbarians 
we have decided to completely stop selling the game because 
