program aimed mainly at minorities from local high schools should 
be safe because other factors besides race are considered but she 
said were just waiting to see what the intent of it the 
ruling is 
the house education and labor committee is to open hearings 
wednesday on the scholarship issue with williams among those 
testifying committee officials said 
