by mimi kennedy its an amazing feat by winters the only 
drawback he doesnt play it for laughs he actually plays it 
straight 
incidentally npr has had a brain wave aimed at helping those 
who dont know the dial location of their local public radio 
station just dial 2028222323 npr says the party at the other 
end will be more than glad to help 
