<TEXT>
the dodge daytona shelby and dodge caravan are 
close in price but far apart when it comes to insurance costs 
according to one insurers annual rating of more than 200 domestic 
and foreign vehicles 
the staid caravan minivan is among the cheapest vehicles to 
insure in the 10000to15000 price range and the sporty shelby 
is among the costliest the allstate insurance co said thursday 
three other chrysler corp minivans the dodge grand caravan 
plymouth voyager turbo and plymouth grand voyager gt and the 
chrysler fifth avenue also ranked among the 10 models with much 
below average insurance costs in their respective price 
categories allstate said 
the list was rounded out by the subaru justy suzuki swift 
toyota tercel ford ltd wagon and the volvo 240 
in addition to the shelby some of the cars rated costliest to 
insure in their respective price classes were the ford escort gt 
geo tracker chevrolet camaro irocz and the bmw 750 series 
the ratings reflect the type of damage a car will suffer in a 
crash repair costs and the cars potential for theft and breakin 
allstate said in a statement from its headquarters in northbrook a 
chicago suburb 
allstate compiled the lists from its experience with collision 
and comprehensive claims on 1989 and 1990 model cars in 45 states 
vehicles with much below average insurance costs generally 
had ratings that were 25 percent to 30 percent below the average 
for their price group said allstate spokesman mike lamonica 
those with much above average costs had ratings that were 25 
percent to 50 percent above the average for their price group he 
said 
chryslers minivans were about 50 percent below average in the 
collision and comprehensive categories lamonica said 
he said the collision data indicate the vehicles withstand 
crashes better than others in their price categories the 
betterthanaverage experience with comprehensive insurance claims 
reflect relatively low theft and vandalism rates 
caravans and voyagers are just not popular theft items 
lamonica said 
demographics also factor into the ratings said allstate 
spokeswoman kathleen hogan owners of chrysler minivans for 
example might tend to be families who live in relatively lowcrime 
areas and drive carefully because they have children in the car 
she said 
chrysler the no 3 domestic automaker sells more minivans than 
another other manufacturer but its dominance is slipping 
chrysler has a tradition of working with insurers to design in 
features to make it easier for crash repair and protection said 
tom jakobowski a company spokesman 
</TEXT>
