donald trumps taj mahal casino 
resort met an extended deadline friday to throw together a 
restructuring agreement and hand it over to state gaming 
regulators 
the developers other two casinos face deadlines saturday to 
make bond payments analysts said one the trump castle probably 
wouldnt make its 184 million payment 
the trump plaza hotel and casino was likely to make its 161 
million bond payment they said both are due by midnight saturday 
the philadelphia inquirer reported in friday editions that trump 
plaza has just 17 million in the bank and trump castle has only 
18 million handy failure to make payments could throw the casinos 
in default and perhaps put them under the protection of bankruptcy 
court 
ed tracy the head of trumps three atlantic city casinos and 
one noncasino hotel would not comment on the status of the bond 
payments tenday grace periods to pay the bonds would not start 
until monday tracy said 
when we have something to say well say it tracy said 
the state casino control commission is only immediately 
concerned with the financial stability of the taj mahal and the 
prepackaged bankruptcy plan it intends to file and leave by 
the spring the commission has said it will likely look at the 
financial stability of the other two properties later 
fridays meeting began 1 hour and 40 minutes late as documents 
arrived at the last minute by facsimile machine attorneys from the 
state the trump organization taj mahal bondholders taj mahal 
subcontractors and banks sought to make sure they all agreed on the 
final terms of the documents 
commission chairman steve perskie stressed as he had in two 
previous hearings that delay in producing the taj mahal documents 
could threaten the license of the 8monthold casino the 
glitziest in atlantic city he had extended his wednesday deadline 
for the deals supporting documents until friday 
i am satisfied that with the submission of documents the 
licensee and other participants have met the conditions imposed by 
the commission perskie said 
the commission recognizes that a lot of people have lost a lot 
of sleep tempers might have been frayed and tensions might have 
been high he said but the public interest is served by 
certainty the schedule was neither arbitrary unfair nor as it 
turns out unreasonable 
state law makes the commission responsible for ensuring that 
each casino licensee remains financially stable the commission has 
the power to take away a license 
the casino commission wants to see the overall agreement by next 
wednesday trump officials have said they intend to file that with 
the federal securities and exchange commission by monday 
perskie said he would rule monday whether documents detailing 
the restructuring agreement should be released to the public other 
documents including certificates of incorporation and new bylaws 
were made public 
the taj mahal failed to make a 473 million payment due nov 15 
to bondholders only to reach a restructuring deal the day after 
the restructuring reduces the interest rate on the 675 million 
in bonds from 14 percent to 12 percent spreads their repayment 
date over ten years instead of eight and gives bondholders half 
ownership in the taj mahal 
trump who has not attended the hearings can raise his 50 
percent ownership to up to 80 percent if he can repay the bonds at 
rates higher than the restructured 12 percent 
the taj mahal has set gross gaming records since its opening 
but it has failed to consistently make the 13 million a day 
that analysts said it needed to break even 
in a market already weakened by the recession the taj mahal has 
siphoned away gaming business from the 11 other casinos including 
trumps other two properties 
raymond neidl a bond analyst with dillon read amp co in new 
york said it does not appear trump castle would make its payment 
leaving open the possibility of a restructuring or bankruptcy 
the market is assuming the payment is not going to be made 
neidl said 
he said the situation looked better for trump plaza which is in 
the center of the boardwalk area and is considered a more 
attractive propoerty than the trump castle 
